name: Master Bed, short distance to Downtown, Fenway
description:
Enjoy a comfortable queen size bed in this Master Bedroom. Room includes 50 Inch Smart TV (Free Netflix/No Cable), a desk, a dresser, and 2 closets.

The space
Single family house located across the street from Roxbury Community College and the Reggie Lewis Athletic center. 75 yards from Roxbury Crossing MBTA Station and 5 minute walk to Northeastern University. 10 minute subway ride to Downtown Boston

The Room itself includes: Tv (Free Netflix), AC, Portable Space Heater, A computer desk with a lamp, a dresser and 2 closets.

Guest access
Guest's have access to a full kitchen, two bathrooms and a very comfortable living room area. Kitchen also includes coffee maker, toaster, and a microwave.

Other things to note
Street Parking: Street cleaning on Tuesdays between 8 AM-12 Noon from April to November

**IMPORTANT NOTICE**

I can NOT accommodate early arrivals or dropping off of luggage ah
